    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[340ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir in your<strong> harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>harissa stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>butter beans</strong></p>",
