      "instruction": "<p>Once the chorizo has crisped, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>and <strong>pepper strips</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> with your <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for a further 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
