      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the<strong> spicy harissa stock</strong> and <strong>drained butter beans </strong>to the pan</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat, then cook for 4-5 min or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>spicy chorizo,</strong> <strong>harissa & butter bean stew</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
